headline: Starbucks Declares Quarterly Cash Dividend
summary: SEATTLE, April 02, 2025--Starbucks Corporation (NASDAQ: SBUX) today announced that its Board of Directors has approved a quarterly cash dividend of $0.61 per share of outstanding Common Stock. The dividend will be payable in cash on May 30, 2025, to shareholders of record on May 16, 2025.
